        <h4 class="p-2 bgd-secondary">
            <i class="fas fa-stethoscope color-primary"></i> Side Effect List
        </h4>
        <p>A side effect can be a harmful and negative outcome that results from blood pressure management.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Low blood pressure or hypotension</li>
            <li>Acute kidney problem (kidneys suddenly not working as well)</li>
            <li>Bradycardia (Slow heart rate)</li>
            <li>Electrolyte problems/metabolic panel (e.g., high/low potassium)</li>
            <li>Hospital visit - initial or prolonged</li>
            <li>A visit to the emergency department</li>
            <li>Dizziness</li>
            <li>Angioedema (swelling under the skin)</li>
            <li>Injurious falls</li>
            <li>Coughing</li>
            <li>Syncope/Loss of consciousness</li>
        </ul>
